name: Baby Shiba Inu
description: Baby Shiba Inu is a novel token with social conscience, built by the dog loving team and fully distributed within the crypto community. Baby Shiba Inu offers an innovative mix of a multi-stage rewards system for staking and NFT presence. Anyone holding the token contributes to a charitable cause as the team is committed to making donations to Shiba Rescue America Organization. Additional profit made from the sale of Baby Shiba Inu merchandise is also donated Shiba Rescue charity.
